feat: add Dolt database health checker (fl-vuq)

Implement CheckDolt() for the database monitoring framework. Performs
four checks: connection ping with latency, query latency via SELECT 1,
commit lag from dolt_log, and orphan database count (testdb_*, beads_t*,
beads_pt*, doctest_* patterns). Configurable commit lag threshold
(default 5min warning) via JSON thresholds field.

